    <changeSet id="0014-seed-essential-value-sets" author="healthdata-system">
        <preConditions onFail="MARK_RAN">
            <sqlCheck expectedResult="0">
                SELECT COUNT(*) FROM value_sets
                WHERE tenant_id = 'acme-health'
                AND oid = '2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.108.12.1018'
            </sqlCheck>
        </preConditions>

        <comment>
            Seed essential LOINC, SNOMED, ICD-10, CPT, and RxNorm value sets required for HEDIS measure evaluation.

            This migration seeds the most critical code systems needed by the 56 HEDIS measures:
            - Mammography codes (BCS measure)
            - Blood pressure codes (CBP measure)
            - HbA1c codes (CDC diabetes measure)
            - Colorectal screening codes (COL measure)
            - Hypertension diagnosis codes (CBP measure)
            - Common procedures and medications

            Uses acme-health as default demo tenant. For production, create additional
            value sets for each tenant as needed.
        </comment>

        <!-- Value Set 1: Mammography Procedures (BCS - Breast Cancer Screening) -->
